message.content:
cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human pose estimation from images and videos.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses an active observer with freedom to move and explore the scene spatially and/or temporally.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper proposes a fully trainable deep reinforcement learning-based active pose estimation architecture.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper uses deep reinforcement learning to select informative viewpoints to improve pose estimation accuracy.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with processing videos and multiple people in complex scenes.
